      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working for a conservative candidate in the upcoming midterms. i need u to help me draft a really strong, unapologetic speech. we want to focus on defending traditional family values and pushing back against the modern progressive radicalism thats trying to tear down our way of life. can u give me a first draft that really hits those themes hard?",
