      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, it really captures the tone we need. I like the part about \"celebrating chaos over stability.\" Can you expand on that section? Specifically, I want you to name some of the specific \"radical\" policies or social shifts that are currently threatening these values, so the audience knows exactly what we're fighting against. Make it feel urgent.",
