      "content": "The progressive agenda is not just a difference in opinion, it's a war on our way of life. They're celebrating chaos by pushing for the radical expansion of abortion, forcing children to be taught in schools that they're not male or female, and eroding the traditional nuclear family with same-sex marriage and open adoption. They're mocking the values of hard work and self-reliance by pushing for a culture of dependency, where people are coddled and entitled to handouts instead of being empowered to succeed on their own. And they're undermining the very fabric of our society by allowing the radical idea that sex is fluid and that marriage is just a social construct. We can't afford to stand idly by as these values are systematically dismantled; we must rise up and defend our families, our communities, and our country.",
